INSTALATION:
------------

Copy the content in /bin folder to your rootfs folder, make sure to have the GPU libraries and driver correctly installed.

CROSS-COMPILING:
------------

1 - Open the ../src/makefile
2 - change the rootfs path
3 - apply the make command on root folder


THE DEMO:
------------

This demos shows a simple opengl es 2.0 usage (10 cubes bouncing around the screen) texturized with data from bitmap files.


TROUBLESHOTS
------------

Make sure to have the images folder in the same folder as the binary. Otherwise errors will occurs. 


